{"tid":372642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自學塔羅求指教！","createTime":"2017-08-24T12:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T13:10:50.000Z","uid":71154,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd095f9b512d4a5f81162580a925ef122776e605","tid":372642,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩抽三張塔羅牌<br />\n問了關於我同佢嘅過去、現在、未來，如下:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">過去: 戰車(正)</span><br />\n之前好有決心，好堅定，而且同佢關係亦充滿挑戰。但同佢欠缺情感嘅交流。<br />\n*暗示有競爭對手(唔知佢係咪有女朋友？)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">現在: 聖杯皇后(正)</span><br />\n關係都好敬重，有愛心，人也好正直。有過快樂時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能佢欣賞我個性，但冇戀愛想法？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">未來: 權杖侍從(正)</span><br />\n大家都係忠誠的人，能信任嘅朋友。<br />\n佢係攜帶重要訊息嘅人<br />\n卡會帶黎好消息？<br />\n<br />\n有咩可以幫我補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b18e5797458730f5ef9eff7b39f03d52289a8ec","tid":372642,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"3146f3a08d24d0b63559829dfab16bac21ff1a2c","tid":372642,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fc37f0453dcc0ad0b8c2cf8241b7051101c5af","tid":372642,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入黎講兩句啦"},{"pid":"628c5e085ee2c41d565b91935ef889c0314f94ff","tid":372642,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"有冇有心人入黎贈我兩句"},{"pid":"11702a14830c439a0711eccd71abc81f3cbd3ad1","tid":372642,"uid":711